#PYTHON PROGRAM TO ADD N NATURAL NUMBERS AND DISPLAY THEIR SUM

a) Using While loop
n=int(input("Enter any natural number here:- "))
sum = 0
a= 1
while a<= n:
    sum = sum + a
    a = a + 1 
print(sum)

b) Using For loop
n=int(input("Enter the natural number here:- "))
sum= 0
for i in range(n+1):
  sum+=i
print(sum)
